Documentation
==============
https://playwright.dev/python/docs/intro

Install
=========
pip install pytest
pip install pytest-playwright

Install the required browsers:
==============================
playwright install


Run test:
===========
pytest <testname.py>

Debug
==========
set PWDEBUG=1
pytest -s -k test_orangehrm.py

Trace
========
set PWDEBUG=0
pytest --tracing on
playwright show-trace test-results\tests-test-orangehrm-py-test-search-employee-chromium\trace.zip
